reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater cute, soft, and of nice quality, with one mentioning it's not scratchy or itchy. The fit receives mixed feedback, with some saying it fits perfectly while others note it runs a little small.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Lady Di Look Alike
items.body: This is absolutely adorable. It is well made and very comfortable. It’s not scratchy or itchy. I would buy this again. Read more
items.author: cdnchick

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Runs true to size
items.body: I love this sweater. It is soft, comfortable and attractive Read more
items.author: Maria Michelon

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Long fibers in yarn
items.body: Such a cute sweater! The only issue is the yarn is loose and therefore it will make small knots or pills easily. I’m disappointed in this item. It’s a spin off of Lady Diana’s jumper from the 80’s. I am keeping it to wear to an 80’s party. Read more
items.author: mrmeber

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute
items.body: It's cute! Very soft and comfortable! I bought the Small/Medium. I normally where Medium. I was hesitant because that means it's going to be on the smaller size, but I didn't want Large/XLarge thinking it might be to big. I'm 5'7 135pounds and 34c. If you want a looser feel go up in size. As far as the white fuzz some people mentioned, if you look at it inside out it's white which kinda gives the appearance of white fuzz, but that's nothing you can do about it and frankly not that noticeable. Read more
items.author: Jade

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars It's a great sweater!
items.body: This sweater is of very nice quality. I was on the fence about ordering it. I'm glad I did. It's made of an acrylic/ wool blend yarn. And yes it is kind of fuzzy, which adds to the charm. The size fit is spot on. Read more
items.author: Anna

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful and Soft
items.body: There weren't many reviews so I wasn't sure but I am so glad I took a chance. This was a splurge for me and I absolutely love this sweater. There wasn't an option for selecting a size so that was confusing. Anyway, I am 5'5 and 127lbs. This sweater is a perfect fit for me. Not loose but a perfect sweater fit. Read more
items.author: I AM SHOPPING

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love and the best price out there!
items.body: Runs a little small Read more
items.author: Heiko Adams

items.title: 1.0 out of 5 stars Fuzzy wuzzie
items.body: Warm sweater but has a weird white fuzz that overlays the whole thing- can’t describe it but it must be something with the white yarn woven into it. Looks like you rolled in cat hair Read more
items.author: FoxJewelryBox

short_description:
Womens Dress is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

To keep it looking sharp, follow the care label first and avoid high heat when drying or steaming if the material is sensitive.

For the best look, smooth the fabric, check the neckline placement, and pair it with shoes that match the occasion and the hem length.

long_description:
Womens Dress is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: One Size.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Color options depend on the listing. Pick the shade that matches your wardrobe for the most repeat wear.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
